room_title: Escape room "The Precinct" by Combo & Key in Portland
room_address: 10160 SW Nimbus Ave, Suite F-2 Portland, OR 97223
room_description:
The Walter Pike Police Department needs your help! A criminal investigation needs to be reopened in order to figure out what really happened! Once you clear the names of the innocent suspects, your next step would be to figure out who actually did it and, most importantly, why!

Comb through evidence and get to the bottom of this incredible case!
